  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at 15th level, when in possession of a weapon that has an unfilled Seal Slot, as an action you may add a Dismantle Seal to that item by spending a Chakra Die. As a free action while casting a Fire Release jutsu of one rank lower than your maximum known, you may pay half the chakra cost rounded up of that jutsu by destroying a weapon with a Dismantle Seal.</p>",
